      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The validation scenario (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending, non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw, Ti-6Al-4V) is sufficiently similar to the COU that extrapolation uncertainty is negligible or quantified.",
      "rationale": "The validation scenario is identical to the COU: same device design, same material, same test standard, same loading mode. No extrapolation is required. The validation activities are considered directly relevant to the COU with no additional uncertainty contribution from domain transfer."
